    <item>
      <title>特鲁多的竞争对手反对提高资本利得税，承诺实施新的减税措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/trudeau-s-rival-opposes-capital-gains-hike-promises-new-tax-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大保守党领袖皮埃尔·波利耶夫 (Pierre Poilievre) 表示，他将投票反对政府提高资本利得税纳入税率的提议，结束了数周以来人们对他在此问题上立场的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/trudeau-s-rival-opposes-capital-gains-hike-promises-new-tax-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 18:44:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西财政部长考虑撤回国会愤怒的税收法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/brazil-finance-chief-weighs-pulling-tax-bill-amid-congress-ire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，巴西财政部长费尔南多·阿达德 (Fernando Haddad) 正考虑撤回一项引起企业和国会愤怒的临时税收措施，因为他试图确保巴西能够实现财政目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/brazil-finance-chief-weighs-pulling-tax-bill-amid-congress-ire</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 18:29:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国向乌克兰运送爱国者导弹和无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/germany-to-deliver-patriot-missiles-strike-drones-to-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为对乌克兰这一饱受战争蹂躏的国家的最新军事援助计划的一部分，德国将向乌克兰运送数千架攻击无人机和 100 枚爱国者导弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/germany-to-deliver-patriot-missiles-strike-drones-to-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 18:02:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登给特朗普贴上重罪犯标签的计划因儿子被定罪而受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/biden-plan-to-brand-trump-a-felon-is-hobbled-by-son-s-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亨特·拜登和唐纳德·特朗普一样，现在也是一名被定罪的重罪犯——这对他的父亲、总统乔·拜登来说是一个个人和政治上的打击，也给他 2024 年的连任竞选带来了困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/biden-plan-to-brand-trump-a-felon-is-hobbled-by-son-s-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 17:49:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约秘书长表示对匈牙利退出乌克兰援助持开放态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/nato-chief-signals-openness-to-hungary-s-opt-out-of-ukraine-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在布达佩斯表示不会深化对基辅的支持后，北约秘书长延斯·斯托尔滕贝格为匈牙利选择不参与对乌克兰的援助计划留下了可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/nato-chief-signals-openness-to-hungary-s-opt-out-of-ukraine-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 17:39:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙的选举赌博引发党内混乱和愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/france-election-macron-s-gamble-triggers-chaos-and-anger-inside-his-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃马纽埃尔·马克龙决定在其政党毫无准备、法国公众也对他避之不及的情况下投入竞选活动，这让他需要赢得选举的那些人感到惊愕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/france-election-macron-s-gamble-triggers-chaos-and-anger-inside-his-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 16:58:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登准备选择戈德史密斯·罗梅罗来领导联邦存款保险公司 (FDIC) 改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/biden-poised-to-pick-goldsmith-romero-to-lead-overhaul-at-fdic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，白宫正准备挑选美国顶级衍生品监管者克里斯蒂·戈德史密斯·罗梅罗来领导联邦存款保险公司的改组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/biden-poised-to-pick-goldsmith-romero-to-lead-overhaul-at-fdic</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 16:56:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国考虑对中国获取人工智能所需芯片施加更多限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/us-weighs-more-limits-on-china-s-access-to-cutting-edge-chips-needed-for-ai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，拜登政府正在考虑进一步限制中国获取用于人工智能的芯片技术，针对的是现在才刚刚进入市场的新硬件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/us-weighs-more-limits-on-china-s-access-to-cutting-edge-chips-needed-for-ai</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 15:43:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特·拜登因枪支指控被特拉华州陪审团裁定有罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/hunter-biden-convicted-of-gun-charges-by-jury-in-delaware-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亨特·拜登被特拉华州联邦法院陪审团裁定枪支指控罪名成立，成为美国现任总统子女中第一位被判犯罪的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/hunter-biden-convicted-of-gun-charges-by-jury-in-delaware-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 15:18:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
